<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1349658-this-is-an-excellent-book-in-vintage-crime">This is an excellent book in vintage crime that starts out a bit soapy, but builds into a well-crafted tale. You will enjoy Mildred and her gang of very descriptive characters. Veda is an opportunistic daughter! Who could blame Mildred for wanting to rid herself of her?</a>
</div>
